  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Centre of Love, a community center serving 500 families provides sanitation facilities, clean water and services in Kibera slums. The majority of people do not have access to sanitation facilities, resulting in improper waste disposal The Centre of Love has been passionately addressing water, sanitation and hygience needs for our community members.  Throughout the world, over 1 million deaths are a result of diseases transmitted via unclean water, poor sanitation and lack of hygiene.</narrative>
  </description>
